svg.text: A Next-Gen Educational Platform for Web Development.
I built AstroShan to replace passive tutorials with immersive 3D simulations.
It turns abstract concepts (DNS, HTTP, HTML) into interactive learning missions.
Tech: Next.js 16, React Three Fiber, MongoDB, Tailwind
• Hybrid Sync Engine: LocalStorage ↔ MongoDB with conflict resolution
• Inclusive 3D Graphics: High-performance WebGL + Canvas fallback
• Gamified Learning: Real-time code validation + progress tracking
